**Input:**

```javascript
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "wildcard": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "Green D*"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])

```

**Output:**

```javascript
{ "title" : "Green Dolphin Street" }
{ "title" : "Green Dragon" }
```

The `$limit` stage limits the results to 5 documents,
while the `$project` stage limits the results to only the
`title` field.

**Input:**

```javascript
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "wildcard": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "Wom?n *"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])

```

**Output:**

```javascript
[
   { title: 'Woman of the Year' },
   { title: 'Woman in a Dressing Gown' },
   { title: 'Women in Love' },
   { title: 'Women on the Verge of a Nervous Breakdown' },
   { title: 'Woman Wanted' }
]
```

The Search Tester might not display all the fields in the
documents it returns. To view all the fields, including the field that
you specify in the query path, expand the document in
the results.

**Input:**

```javascript
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "wildcard": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "*\\?"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])

```

**Output:**

```javascript
{ "title" : "Where Are My Children?" }
{ "title" : "Who Killed Cock Robin?" }
{ "title" : "What's Opera, Doc?" }
{ "title" : "Will Success Spoil Rock Hunter?" }
{ "title" : "Who Was That Lady?" }
```

